page_title: 'Quickstart: Use Azure OpenAI Service with the JavaScript SDK and the completions API'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI and make your first completions call with the Go SDK.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free- Go 1.21.0 or higher installed locally.- An Azure OpenAI Service resource with the `gpt-35-turbo` model deployed. For more information about model deployment, see the resource deployment guide.
